list.title: cacheUrlFetchApp
list.description: Checks if the return from a Url fetch is in cache. If so, retrieves it from cache instead of making another network request. If not, makes a new request and adds it to the cache.

list.title: getData
list.description: Takes as input a table name, a table address, and a toggle for using the cache service. If a table name and a table address are boh provided, the script will use the address. The response is parsed as JSON on the return.
